1)How can I get the list of files in a directory using C/C++?
  #include<stdio.h>
  int main()
  {
   char command[20] = "ls -l";
   system(command);
   return 0;
   }
   
2) How to debug a core in C/C++?
 A process dumps core when it is terminated by operating system due to fault in program.The most common fault is that program accessing invalid pointer(NNULL) or value out area of memory
